{"tid":1643426,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[自行判斷] 中出羊子：為何不需買VPN！","createTime":"2019-10-10T06:21:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T06:22:32.000Z","uid":121869,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"34d6facc9475a3d823393018e9ebf5fc917426ed","tid":1643426,"uid":121869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"TLDR:<br />\n- 全面封網的話VPN都冇用<br />\n- 如果DNS做手腳嚟封網的話可善用DNS over TLS功能<br />\n- ISP 同網路上嘅監聽者都能會見到你瀏覽嘅每個網站&amp;App 可以揀買VPN/用1.1.1.1<br />\n- 驚閪政府封網呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大不了攬炒<br />\n- 唔好down來力不明/背景模糊嘅VPN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">         &middot;對匿名無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n         &middot;小心比人出賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div>- 清楚了解VPN service provider先好比錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">         &middot;貪express/其他vpn平嘅我建議你重新考慮<br />\n         &middot;嫌麻煩唔知邊個信得過嘅買返Nord啦</div><br />\n- 唔怕封網但有需要匿名上網嘅我都係建議你地買VPN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 和理優冇需要匿名嘅用1.1.1.1+WARP都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">(自行判斷)</div><br />\n</span><br />\n//<br />\n羊：<span style=\"color: red;\">現代萬維網強烈依賴CDN，唯一封鎖特定網站(如鬼登)而不影響其餘65534個網站的唯一方法，就是在DNS做手腳</span>，故有人說，政府可以鎖DNS來達到封鎖特定網站(如鬼登)目的。很不幸，<span style=\"color: gold;\">Andriod9已早預備DNS over TLS功能，只要簡單設置，就能解析得到CDN IP地址</span>，不需用上VPN如此耗電而昂貴方案。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">故此現實是特區政府+黨中央要是無法用強力部門取締鬼登，則只能全面封網</span>，連登傻仔花千幾蚊買回來的三年<span style=\"color: red;\">VPN，到時也是不會用得著。</span><br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n有網友問要不要買定VPN，我的答案是不需要，現時的VPN技術，大多都是Connection Oriented，需要建立一個持久的連線來維持狀態和更新金鑰(也為了穿越NAT)，並不適合現代智能手機出街環境使用，用起來會非常食電。<br />\n<br />\n#世界百大VPN中29家為六家中國公司所持有<br />\n<br />\nCloudflare 的WARP，聽說有解決傳統VPN技術智能手機環境耗電問題，只此一家，可參考 https://1.1.1.1/ ，但<span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>情況不同大陸，在<span style=\"color: red;\">大量依賴CDN服務的現今網絡生態下，特區正苦要封鎖特定網站，只能整個CDN封殺</span>，意即必然會殃及池魚(封鬼登=封852郵報+輔仁+立場新聞+熱血時報+無限多企業網站)，而且鬼登絕對不會是封網對像，親中傳媒甚至沒半句批評，原因耐人尋味，答案你我早知。<br />\n<br />\nVPN什麼的，一句講晒，不用晒錢。<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中出羊子啲content係有佢嘅價值但亦都不斷叫人去同泛民、和理非、學社本土、港獨派甚至Lihkg等等分割，淨係得城邦派先信信得過。啲文十篇有八篇係搞分化。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁做咩我要做暖氣軍師share佢啲post呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事關近日禁網風吹得好勁，怕各位手足download啲鬼VPN 比中共監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.computerweekly.com/news/252466203/Top-VPNs-secretly-owned-by-Chinese-firms\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.computerweekly.com%2Fnews%2F252466203%2FTop-VPNs-secretly-owned-by-Chinese-firms&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=27867a9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.computerweekly.com/news/252466203/Top-VPNs-secretly-owned-by-Chinese-firms</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BWtK2cC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBWtK2cC.jpg&h=fd4fb8e7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AqWD6Ei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAqWD6Ei.jpg&h=fe54d117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=o06WQStWlOE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Do06WQStWlOE&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=1271ce52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=o06WQStWlOE</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋認為有需要匿名上網嘅手足我都係建議你哋買返個VPN account雖然全面封網可能用唔着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信大部份覺得NordVPN貴嘅手足都會留意過甚至已經買咗ExpressVPN但上網睇過雖然ExpressVPN係BVI公司，但其實係港資仲好可能背後係中資嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾年前喺大陸仲會自動降加密強度安唔安全大<br />\n家自行衡量啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techinasia.com/china-vpn-safe-expressvpn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techinasia.com%2Fchina-vpn-safe-expressvpn&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=3141c045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.techinasia.com/china-vpn-safe-expressvpn</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://slate.com/technology/2019/02/best-vpn-companies-trust-privacy.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fslate.com%2Ftechnology%2F2019%2F02%2Fbest-vpn-companies-trust-privacy.html&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=eb62042f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://slate.com/technology/2019/02/best-vpn-companies-trust-privacy.html</a><br />\n溫馨提示：VPN供應商能查閱/轉交用戶日誌給權威機構 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(小心俾人出賣啊）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔使匿名上網嘅和理優手足1.1.1.1+WARP<br />\n都夠你哋用嘅（如果冇打算俾錢買VPN的話）<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/10/03/warpvpncaution/tech-secure\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F10%2F03%2Fwarpvpncaution%2Ftech-secure&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=e78ac9c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/10/03/warpvpncaution/tech-secure</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/09/26/cloudflarevpn/tech-secure\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F09%2F26%2Fcloudflarevpn%2Ftech-secure&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em7uZPUOKbERJWvoN25G5CUI%3D&h=f9eb7043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/09/26/cloudflarevpn/tech-secure</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n民族自強 港人自救<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<br />\n六大訴求 缺一不可</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">香港人 反抗</div>"},{"pid":"f5bdf6e321aa81b17e1578b90452b6ecb459ea6b","tid":1643426,"uid":279932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T06:22:32.000Z","msg":"NordVPN原來算貴架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}